    </div>
    <button class="hint-toggle" onclick="showHintQFT('h12')">show hint</button>
    <div class="feedback hint" id="h12">F₂ = (1/√2)·((1,1),(1,−1)) = H (Hadamard). The 2-point DFT is exactly the Hadamard gate!</div>
    <div class="feedback" id="fb12"></div>
  </div>
</div>
